# @afenda/docs — Fumadocs documentation site
#
# No runtime environment variables are required for build or deploy.
# This app is intentionally isolated from ERP auth, database, and CSP secrets.
#
# Local dev:
#   pnpm --filter @afenda/docs dev    # http://localhost:3001
#
# Do NOT copy ERP secrets from apps/erp/.env.local into this project.
# Vercel docs project: use a separate Vercel project with Root Directory = apps/docs.
